title: Ep 16 - Decide What You Want
itunes:title: Ep 16 - Decide What You Want
description:
What do you want? In order to get everything you want from this life we must decide, in detail, what it is that we want in our life. Most people have an idea of what they want, but don't have 100% clarity. In this episode we speak about finding and following your passion in order to have a happy life.
